5ca79be5b4541a6bde8f08d0df2b25618b61e","tid":330610,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下 咁你咪帶口罩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係諗住叫個病人帶口罩下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前返PT, 有條友病左唔帶口罩, 最後傳染左比我<br />\n我話佢唔帶口罩, 佢調返轉頭屌我身體差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢D真係冚家剷<br />\n完全不知所謂<br />\n好似D蝗咁屌返你轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88de7521a5710200758185c1665e68e7558fc31","tid":330610,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"唔帶咪好 感染班死廢老<br />\n佢地免疫力咁弱<br />\n求其中下招又死一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b168faf46ff9f68e53e17614fa8cfaf527c4a775","tid":330610,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以我一直都係自己隨身袋幾個口罩<br />\n搭車嗰陣一有人咳即刻戴</blockquote><br />\n唉<br />\n所以香港真係好撚反智<br />\n有病嗰個唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迫冇病嗰個戴</blockquote><br />\n係得香港咁on9 人地國家都係病人唔會戴</blockquote><br />\n因為口罩就係用嚟防止病毒傳開去 而防唔到病毒傳入 N92嗰種強力口罩就唔知啦 但至少最普通嗰種係用嚟防傳出而唔係防傳入<br />\n<br />\n無病嗰個戴無用 要有病嗰個戴先有用 點解哩個post包括樓主都好似無經歷過沙士 豬流感咁 定係咁快唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459adde33d62ef22516917571a986043491bd264","tid":330610,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以我一直都係自己隨身袋幾個口罩<br />\n搭車嗰陣一有人咳即刻戴</blockquote><br />\n唉<br />\n所以香港真係好撚反智<br />\n有病嗰個唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迫冇病嗰個戴</blockquote><br />\n係得香港咁on9 人地國家都係病人唔會戴</blockquote><br />\n因為口罩就係用嚟防止病毒傳開去 而防唔到病毒傳入 N92嗰種強力口罩就唔知啦 但至少最普通嗰種係用嚟防傳出而唔係防傳入<br />\n<br />\n無病嗰個戴無用 要有病嗰個戴先有用 點解哩個post包括樓主都好似無經歷過沙士 豬流感咁 定係咁快唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通外科口罩適用於患感冒時進出不通風場所，如診所、戲院等，保護自己之餘亦可防飛沬傳播病菌。普通外科口罩只可使用一次，如發現口罩有破損、弄濕或弄污，都應該立即更換。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1450893/%E6%88%B4%E9%8C%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%98%B2%E9%8C%AF%E8%8F%8C%20%20%20N95%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1450893%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E9%258C%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%258F%258C%2520%2520%2520N95%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25EF%25BC%259F&d=FvFA8ojCvdVcNNfXNVqDURv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0dda680b\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1450893/%E6%88%B4%E9%8C%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%98%B2%E9%8C%AF%E8%8F%8C%20%20%20N95%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"e2974e2cc6762e3f1a502dfcbc4e6b17ae1c7434","tid":330610,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所以我一直都係自己隨身袋幾個口罩<br />\n搭車嗰陣一有人咳即刻戴</blockquote><br />\n唉<br />\n所以香港真係好撚反智<br />\n有病嗰個唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 迫冇病嗰個戴</blockquote><br />\n係得香港咁on9 人地國家都係病人唔會戴</blockquote><br />\n因為口罩就係用嚟防止病毒傳開去 而防唔到病毒傳入 N92嗰種強力口罩就唔知啦 但至少最普通嗰種係用嚟防傳出而唔係防傳入<br />\n<br />\n無病嗰個戴無用 要有病嗰個戴先有用 點解哩個post包括樓主都好似無經歷過沙士 豬流感咁 定係咁快唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通外科口罩適用於患感冒時進出不通風場所，如診所、戲院等，保護自己之餘亦可防飛沬傳播病菌。普通外科口罩只可使用一次，如發現口罩有破損、弄濕或弄污，都應該立即更換。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1450893/%E6%88%B4%E9%8C%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%98%B2%E9%8C%AF%E8%8F%8C%20%20%20N95%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1450893%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E9%258C%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%258C%25AF%25E8%258F%258C%2520%2520%2520N95%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25EF%25BC%259F&d=FvFA8ojCvdVcNNfXNVqDURv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0dda680b\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1450893/%E6%88%B4%E9%8C%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%98%B2%E9%8C%AF%E8%8F%8C%20%20%20N95%E6%9C%80%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%EF%BC%9F</a></blockquote><br />\n呢個好似講得好D<br />\n<br />\n醫療手術口罩約可以過濾八～九成的病毒微粒，但要注意配戴方法，確定區別正反面，不是依顏色看正反面，而是要看材質，防水層是在外側，布面是貼近口鼻處。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.commonhealth.com.tw/article/article.action?nid=61767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.commonhealth.com.tw%2Farticle%2Farticle.action%3Fnid%3D61767&d=FvFA8ojCvdVcNNfXNVqDURv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e1bd9245\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.commonhealth.com.tw/article/article.action?nid=61767</a>"},{"pid":"c14cf3382ec54ba65c0a073cdeedca5d1c551740","tid":330610,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"好難呼吸"},{"pid":"8c5a7b52e6cfee48c0d65a02c0947b7737c0811e","tid":330610,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難呼吸</blockquote><br />\n病咗就梗係難呼吸河<br />\n咪咁自私啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6ae83ed8771d621bb26aa9b5f55073b160013a","tid":330610,"uid":68091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係無病果個帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1764be4add0702268e61053681a1b361bcd5c1","tid":330610,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲都係無病果個帶<img src=\"